episodes.title: The Ann Harder Show - Keith Brown, Author and Cult survivor, Music by Robby Abel
episodes.description: Keith Brown, Cult survivor and author of Counterfeit Culture, about her escape from what she believes is a cult and how it's affected her and her family's lives. We get some great music from Robby Abel, and a new Act Locally Waco with Elizabeth Riley. Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices
